drinking coffee alone, as always.

165
00:12:41,824 --> 00:12:43,409
But I wasn't around.

166
00:12:45,328 --> 00:12:47,288
I thought that'd make you more lonely.

167
00:12:49,123 --> 00:12:50,750
[♪ soft music playing]

168
00:12:53,836 --> 00:12:56,130
From the looks of it, I guess I was right.

169
00:13:00,134 --> 00:13:01,135
Thank you.

170
00:13:02,553 --> 00:13:03,554
For what?

171
00:13:06,349 --> 00:13:10,603
You know, for looking out for me, I guess.

172
00:13:11,396 --> 00:13:12,814
I wouldn't call it that.

173
00:13:13,648 --> 00:13:15,900
I don't know. Mmm.

174
00:13:15,983 --> 00:13:17,610
I guess you keep getting to me.

175
00:13:19,195 --> 00:13:20,655
So weird, right?

176
00:13:22,323 --> 00:13:23,324
What do you mean?

177
00:13:25,243 --> 00:13:27,245
How we're on each other's minds.

178
00:13:28,955 --> 00:13:30,790
And we barely know each other.

179
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:33,668
I think it's weird.

180
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:36,754
I don't get why I think about you so much.

181
00:13:38,714 --> 00:13:42,885
About how you're always alone,
how you're always eating alone…

182
00:13:44,345 --> 00:13:46,055
But mostly, I keep thinking

183
00:13:47,515 --> 00:13:50,268
how lonely you'd be when I'm not around.

184
00:13:53,729 --> 00:13:56,107
I don't want to think
about any of that anymore.

185
00:13:59,902 --> 00:14:01,237
Will you be my boyfriend?

186
00:14:30,016 --> 00:14:31,976
[driver] I'm going to your wife now.

187
00:14:33,269 --> 00:14:35,354
I'm so angry and upset right now

188
00:14:36,439 --> 00:14:38,816
that I'm going to shred her to pieces.

189
