-W-Wait, sir. Just…
-[phone beeps]

190
00:14:43,196 --> 00:14:44,405
INCOMING CALL
FATHER-IN-LAW

191
00:14:44,488 --> 00:14:48,201
H-Hey! Wait. Wait a minute, sir.

192
00:14:48,784 --> 00:14:51,913
Look, I wasn't able
to reach my father-in-law,

193
00:14:51,996 --> 00:14:54,207
but he's calling me back right now.
STYLE
::cue()

194
00:14:54,290 --> 00:14:58,419
I can actually get you the money you want.
I promise. I swear.

195
00:14:58,502 --> 00:14:59,629
Are you kidding?

196
00:15:00,630 --> 00:15:02,381
You want another chance?

197
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:08,095
I mean, have you no shame at all?

198
00:15:08,596 --> 00:15:10,723
I've given you so many chances already.

199
00:15:11,432 --> 00:15:12,433
You want another one?

200
00:15:12,516 --> 00:15:15,019
Yes, please j-just once.

201
00:15:15,937 --> 00:15:18,314
Give me a chance
to make up for what I've done.

202
00:15:21,108 --> 00:15:22,401
Don't do this, boss.

203
00:15:22,485 --> 00:15:25,154
No, please, wait. Please, sir! Just once!

204
00:15:25,238 --> 00:15:27,907
Please, just give me
one last chance, okay?

205
00:15:27,990 --> 00:15:30,826
Geez, you're making this so hard.

206
00:15:44,674 --> 00:15:47,093
You know, once at my old job,

207
00:15:47,176 --> 00:15:50,263
I made a few mistakes that
I could've been fired over, but I wasn't.

208
00:15:51,514 --> 00:15:53,766
Later, I asked the boss
why he didn't fire me,

209
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,977
and he said…

210
00:15:58,229 --> 00:15:59,230
"Look, man."

211
00:16:00,106 --> 00:16:03,943
"Everyone deserves at least three chances
to be the best version of themselves."

212
00:16:06,570 --> 00:16:09,573
And it's not like harming your wife
will make me feel any better.

213
00:16:11,075 --> 00:16:12,285
So, Mr. Kang?

214
00:16:13,369 --> 00:16:15,121
This really is your last chance.

215
00:16:15,204 --> 00:16:16,580
Right, sir.

216
00:16:17,665 --> 00:16:20,710
I appreciate it. Thank you.
Thank you so much.

217
00:16:20,793 --> 00:16:22,545
I'm giving you a chance,

218
00:16:22,628 --> 00:16:25,965
but there will be compensation
for you breaking my heart, right?

219
00:16:26,048 --> 00:16:28,551
Yes. Of course there will be.

220
00:16:29,468 --> 00:16:30,845
Two billion won.

221
00:16:30,928 --> 00:16:31,929
Pardon?

222
00:16:33,431 --> 00:16:34,432
Two billion.

223
00:16:34,515 --> 00:16:36,642
Geez, is the line bad or something?

224
00:16:37,685 --> 00:16:38,978
No.

225
00:16:40,104 --> 00:16:41,814
I heard you. Two billion won.

226
00:16:41,897 --> 00:16:43,232
I'll give you two hours,

227
00:16:44,108 --> 00:16:45,985
but if you go back on your word,

228
00:16:46,068 --> 00:16:50,865
