Yes, Father.

236
00:17:13,387 --> 00:17:15,973
We need to talk. It's about Seyun.

237
00:17:20,019 --> 00:17:22,521
[♪ dramatic music playing]

238
00:17:39,455 --> 00:17:42,291
[grunts, breathes heavily]

239
00:17:48,547 --> 00:17:49,548
