-[metal rattles]
-[yelps, groans]

242
00:18:16,742 --> 00:18:17,952
[groans]

243
00:18:30,673 --> 00:18:31,841
[grunts]

244
00:18:31,924 --> 00:18:33,384
[breathing heavily]
STYLE
::cue()

245
00:18:45,688 --> 00:18:48,232
-[Dr. Ko groans]
-[gasps]

246
00:18:48,983 --> 00:18:51,402
-Are you okay, Mother?
-[gasps]

247
00:18:51,902 --> 00:18:52,903
